I was...

01:49:44.000 --> 01:49:47.000
I had been... We had been talking about the change in the...

01:49:47.000 --> 01:49:49.000
the diversity of commission and...

01:49:49.000 --> 01:49:50.000
The former guy in the school.

01:49:50.000 --> 01:49:51.000
And women...

01:49:51.000 --> 01:49:52.000
Women and the...

