01:50:20.000 --> 01:50:23.000
He's a Ranger too, my son.

01:50:23.000 --> 01:50:25.000
Hey, they just got through.

01:50:25.000 --> 01:50:28.000
And I walked back in, just smiling and said,

01:50:28.000 --> 01:50:30.000
I just got the best news you can think of.

01:50:30.000 --> 01:50:31.000
My son called me and said,

01:50:31.000 --> 01:50:35.000
Those two rangers, female, just got through.

01:50:35.000 --> 01:50:39.000
And there were maybe 15 of us, 20...

01:50:39.000 --> 01:50:41.000
Except for this colonel.

01:50:41.000 --> 01:50:42.000
Ha!

01:50:42.000 --> 01:50:43.000
Enough for much of what's up.

01:50:43.000 --> 01:50:45.000
West being lesbian.

01:50:45.000 --> 01:50:46.000
And I blew up.

01:50:46.000 --> 01:50:48.000
I went one on a table, he's the other end.

01:50:48.000 --> 01:50:50.000
And how, when the hell can you say that?

01:50:50.000 --> 01:50:52.000
They're qualified, they've proved it.

01:50:52.000 --> 01:50:54.000
And these civilians say,

01:50:54.000 --> 01:50:57.000
I mean civilians, they're these non-army type...

01:50:57.000 --> 01:51:00.000
They're listening to this.

01:51:00.000 --> 01:51:03.000
