01:51:13.000 --> 01:51:16.000
And he now...

01:51:16.000 --> 01:51:19.000
And my wife, a cute, being...

01:51:19.000 --> 01:51:21.000
In a probic, I just refused to talk to him,

01:51:21.000 --> 01:51:23.000
Except to say hello.

01:51:23.000 --> 01:51:25.000
