01:51:27.000 --> 01:51:29.000
And that's what we're expecting.

01:51:29.000 --> 01:51:30.000
That's what we want them to do.

01:51:30.000 --> 01:51:35.000
And so to answer your question, yes, I've faced that.

01:51:35.000 --> 01:51:37.000
