01:52:09.000 --> 01:52:11.000
A year and a half ago.

01:52:11.000 --> 01:52:15.000
And he had to do it so pretty well.

01:52:15.000 --> 01:52:20.000
Leo, the father, is retired.

01:52:20.000 --> 01:52:21.000
Brigadier.

01:52:21.000 --> 01:52:27.000
His other son is a retired two star, one star.

01:52:27.000 --> 01:52:33.000
