02:00:38.000 --> 02:00:41.000
I'd be happy to tell him that you refused to give it to me.

02:00:41.000 --> 02:00:42.000
No, I'll tell you.

02:00:42.000 --> 02:00:45.000
So he gave me a look at the crew served weapons.

02:00:45.000 --> 02:00:49.000
I report that back to the my boss.

02:00:49.000 --> 02:00:51.000
General, he went up and reported the chief of staff.

02:00:51.000 --> 02:00:58.000
We're talking, it's still sensitive to race because I was about it.

